summary: It's official guys. I'm a sticker girl. I have a total of 21 stickers currently. (One has three different variants xD;) I went...
caption:
It’s official guys. I’m a sticker girl. I have a total of 21 stickers currently. (One has three different variants xD;) I went out and bought a little box to hold all of them on my table because I just had too many! I went to buy them at like 11:00PM. Who knew so many people would be shopping at that time too? Some people were in their pajamas, so I was really like “why are you even here??” I can’t really talk since I was out shopping at 11:00PM too… xD;

I included my latest stickers! I wanted a kitty, so I drew one. I did the lineart and flats on my stream (www.twitch.tv/operationugawts). I wasn’t sure how to decorate it, so I pulled from my cheshire cat inspiration. x]

The eel should be familiar! I’m working on adding more punch to his overall picture, but he just screamed to be a sticker. I printed him out and now he’s alive!

The gamer controller was also taken from a larger piece I did a while back. I redid the lineart and coloring. I realized once the sticker was in my hand that the tears going upward can be confusing out of context, so I’m going to be redoing those.

I’m slowly adding products to my shop:
tictail.com/opugawts

I did a photoshoot with most of my stickers. I just need to edit the pictures.
I also have a redbubble store: redbubble.com/people/opugawts

summary: Look, im so introvert that its really strange/frightening for me to interact with people on the internet, but im going yo try to...
body:
Look, im so introvert that its really strange/frightening for me to interact with people on the internet, but im going yo try to be more open here, we are almost 100 and i want to know how many of you are not pornbots, if we make It to 100 before the year ends ill make a doodle comision for each of you.

Also this means that ill write more stuff about anything, from movies to projects and feelings, i just want to know what you all like, and to you yo know me a bit better.

To end this, i would love to read some feedback or comments.

Thanks for everything.
